             THEN `BOTTOM_FREE (TAKE_FIRSTN (CLOCK c) (LENGTH v1) l)`
                   by PROVE_TAC[BOTTOM_FREE_TAKE_FIRSTN]
             THEN IMP_RES_TAC
                   (GSYM
                    (ISPECL[``CLOCK c``,``LENGTH(v1:'a letter list)``]
